    <section class="faq">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">When do I need to RSVP by?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Please RSVP no later than August 30th via the website. If there are issues in trying to RSVP, please reach out.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">What should I wear?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Dress code is semi-formal. Think garden party vibes â€” dressy but comfortable!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">Can I bring a guest?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes, all guests are either invited alongside someone or allowed to bring a plus one. If your invitation was sent to you and you only,
                        feel free to invite someone. Please reach out if you have any questions regarding this!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">Where should I stay?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>We have reserved a small number of room blocks at a few hotels you can find on the Details page of the website. However, please look at
                        all your options and choose whatever works best for you! Please read on the details page for more information.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">Is there parking at the venue?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes, there is some parking at the venue for about 20 cars. However, ubers and lyfts will be easy to come by in the area.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

